### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Solar potential - Lagos, Nigeria (PVWatts)
GET http://localhost:8080/solar/potential?lat=6.5244&lon=3.3792&tilt=20&azimuth=180

### Solar estimate - Lagos, Nigeria (uses PVWatts internally)
POST http://localhost:8080/solar/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 6.5244,
  "longitude": 3.3792,
  "panel_wattage": 450,
  "panel_count": 12
}

