### Solar potential - London, UK (lower solar resource example)
GET http://localhost:8080/solar/potential?lat=51.5074&lon=-0.1278&tilt=35&azimuth=180

### Solar estimate - London, UK (lower solar resource example)
POST http://localhost:8080/solar/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 51.5074,
  "longitude": -0.1278,
  "panel_wattage": 400,
  "panel_count": 8,
  "panel_tilt": 35,
  "azimuth": 180
}

### Solar forecast - Lagos, Nigeria (Open-Meteo)
GET http://localhost:8080/solar/forecast?lat=6.5244&lon=3.3792&panel_wattage=450&panel_count=12
